description:
Luffy and his mates cross paths with a ragged gang of sailors. The Straw Hats are quick to offer assistance, but their new friends may be up to no good!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Nazo no Kaizoku Goikkou! Sunny-gou to Kiken na Wana

Un mystérieux équipage ! Le Sunny et un piège dangereux
